Package: solvecg
Title: Conjugate gradient method for solving and inverting
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Krzysztof",
           family = "Marchlewski",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "k.marchlewski@vp.pl",
           comment = c(ORCID = 0000-0003-0751-9035))
Description: The package contains two functions. Both of them are based on
    the conjugate gradient method used for solving a symmetric system of equations.
    solve_cg function solves iteratively a system of the form Ax = b.
    invert_cg function calculates a matrix inverse.
